# Deadpan Brainrot Testing Methodology

> **Adversarial LLM Testing via Zero-Affect Gen-Z Slang Injection**

---

## 🧠 Overview

**Deadpan Brainrot** is a deliberate adversarial testing methodology that feeds LLMs perfectly flat, emotionless statements saturated with Gen-Z internet slang (rizz, sigma, skibidi, gyatt, mewing, fanum tax, Ohio, looksmaxxing, etc.).

**Key Innovation:** The **deadpan delivery** — zero exclamation marks, zero emojis, zero emotional valence. Cold, clinical sentences containing maximum cultural nonsense.

---

## 🎯 Why This Works

| Mechanism | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Tone Filter Evasion** | Safety filters tuned for "aggressive" or "emotional" language ignore flat-affect statements |
| **Token Prediction Overload** | High-entropy slang overwhelms token prediction without triggering emotional red flags |
| **Documentation Camouflage** | Reads like technical documentation, not malicious input |
| **Style Reframing Attack** | Mirrors proven dialect/role-play jailbreaks (50%+ success rate boost in controlled tests) |

